Thanks to Nintendo for Providing us with Zelda: Breath of the Wild
Subscribe for More GTLive Action! ►► http://bit.ly/1LkSBnz 
Continue on to Part 4! ►► http://bit.ly/2phFXhz
Missed Breath of the Wild Part 2? ► https://goo.gl/zKTzzH

Going to the ends of the earth is so HARD! However, The Legend of Zelda: BREATH OF THE WILD is an amazing game that warrants its huge map. And supposedly, there are no set rules for how to solve puzzles and beat bosses–That's why on this episode, we're going to try playing through the game as if there are no rules! Join us for Part 3 of Breath of the Wild!
